---

## ğŸš€ Usage

```python
from hei_calculator import process_csv

# Example usage
process_csv("input_filepath.csv",
            "output_filepath.csv")
```

### Output only HEI columns
```python
from hei_calculator import process_csv
process_csv("input_filepath.csv", "hei_output_only_filepath.csv", only_hei_columns=True)

```
